              "message": "=Extract details as:\n-event: find what made the client talk\n  with us, extract only as this strings:\n  \"reservation\" or \"cancellation\"\n-booking_id: find the number reference\n  to the order booking id extract as \n  number in string type\n  instead\n-name: find the name of the client,\n\nAll informationmust be\nfrom the following\ntext and ONLY from this text:\n{{ $json.message.text }}\n "
